data.description: You will fall in love with this beautiful Westnedge hill neighborhood 3 BR, 1 full bath home with over 1200 finished square feet of living space. Beautiful kitchen cabinetry and soft close drawers, granite counter tops, SS refrigerator, range, microwave, dishwasher (all are only 2 yrs old), hardwood laminate flooring throughout the main floor. Spacious eating area and LR.  Private primary bedroom located on the upper floor is complete with a 12' x 12' walk in closet. Improvements include a 2 car detached garage, newer windows & flooring on mail level, & carpeting upstairs, all newer plumbing, electrical, C/A, block vented windows in the basement; single vanity and acrylic tub/shower surround in the bathroom, repainted throughout.  Kalamazoo Schools.
